    "excerpt": "Telkom-Siemens Centre of Excellence collaboration theme.",
    "shell": "default",
    "meta": {},
    "html": "<h2>Broadband Networks and Applications</h2>\n<p>The research page includes the Stellenbosch unit of the Telkom-Siemens Centre of Excellence in ATM and Broadband Networks and their Applications.</p>\n<p>Its stated aims include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>promoting R&amp;D in broadband technologies and applications</li>\n<li>training postgraduate students and professionals in telecommunications expertise</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Members listed on source page</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Jaco Geldenhuys</li>\n<li>Anthony E Krzesinski</li>\n<li>Willem Visser</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Source: <a href=\"https://cs.sun.ac.za/research/\">https://cs.sun.ac.za/research/</a></p>\n",
